Product name: 1930s Black Sheer Formal Ginger Rogers Big Ruffled Bottom Hardly Worn Size Medium
Description:
WAIST: 27-28 INCHES SMALL TO MEDIUM WAIST
Absolutely the most beautiful black sheer dress ever! Ginger Rogers dance style bottom.  Very full with ruffles dividing each skirt seam.   Bottom has 12 of these ruffles sewn around the bottom.  Makes for a lovely full skirt.  The shoulders have these fabulous ruffles also(see picture).   The bodice neck is gathered for fullness in the bust and a little more mystery cover. There are snaps and hook and eye on the side and the back has a single hook and eye at neck with a long deep slit.  Not enough pictures to show this. This is a beautiful dress. There is no label. I have pinned this on my mannequin for best look. Please measure yourself for best fit. The slip that you can see under dress is not included.  Just wanted you you see detail.
